<section id="context_keyman">
  <title>Keyman Desktop Configuration</title>
  <para>To open Keyman Configuration:<orderedlist><listitem><para>Click on the <application>Keyman Desktop</application> icon<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="images\tray_01.png"></imagedata></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>in the system tray.</para><para>A menu is displayed:</para><para><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="images\menu.png"></imagedata></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></para></listitem><listitem><para>From the menu select Configuration or click on the title, Keyman Desktop 7.0, to display the Keyman Configuration window. </para><para><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="images\context_configuration_tabs_01.png"></imagedata></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></para></listitem></orderedlist></para>
  <para>Keyman Configuration is used to install keyboard layouts, modify <application>Keyman Desktop</application> options, configure hotkeys and language layouts and activate <application>Keyman Desktop</application>.</para>
  <para>For more information on these functions, please see:<itemizedlist><listitem><para><xref linkend="context_configuration_keyboards"></xref></para></listitem><listitem><para><xref linkend="context_configuration_options"></xref></para></listitem><listitem><para><xref linkend="context_configuration_hotkeys"></xref></para></listitem><listitem><para><xref linkend="context_configuration_addins"></xref></para></listitem><listitem><para><xref linkend="context_configuration_languages"></xref></para></listitem><listitem><para><xref linkend="context_configuration_support"></xref></para></listitem><listitem><para><xref linkend="context_activate"></xref></para></listitem></itemizedlist></para>
